WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:02.732
Previously on Empire...

00:02.756 --> 00:03.922
I'm sorry.

00:03.923 --> 00:06.746
What you have there is
an injunction ordering you

00:06.747 --> 00:08.658
to allow the Empire Trust Tour
to continue.

00:08.682 --> 00:11.728
- Cookie, I'm pregnant.
- What?

00:11.752 --> 00:14.297
The Feds are after you.
Watch your back.

00:14.321 --> 00:16.967
The chemo drugs I took
destroyed my heart muscle.

00:16.991 --> 00:18.768
I'm gonna end my life, Pop.

00:18.792 --> 00:21.838
You don't have to do this. I love you.

00:21.862 --> 00:23.273
I love you, too.

00:23.297 --> 00:24.508
Andre! Andre!

00:24.532 --> 00:26.965
Andre! Andre! Andre!

00:28.936 --> 00:30.847
COOKIE: Andre, please don't go. Andre.

00:30.871 --> 00:32.482
- Andre, Andre!
- Oh, no.

00:32.506 --> 00:35.620
- What do we got?
- NURSE: Unresponsive male, not breathing.

00:35.621 --> 00:37.766
- Been down 30 minutes.
- COOKIE: Oh, Andre!

00:37.790 --> 00:40.135
- Starting amiodarone. - There's no pulse.
- (MONITOR FLATLINING)

00:40.159 --> 00:43.005
- No.
- All right, charging 200.

00:43.029 --> 00:44.673
- Andre!
- Clear.

00:44.697 --> 00:46.608
- Hands off. Clear. - Shocking.
- (ELECTRICAL THUMP)

00:46.632 --> 00:48.276
- Please. Please!
- Checking for rhythm.

00:48.300 --> 00:51.279
LUCIOUS: Come on, Andre,
come on, come on.

00:51.303 --> 00:53.115
COOKIE: Oh, my God.

00:53.139 --> 00:55.719
- DOCTOR: Do we have a rhythm?
- (MONITOR CONTINUES FLATLINING)

00:57.343 --> 00:59.021
- Andre...
- Shock him again.

00:59.045 --> 01:01.957
- Shock him again! Shock him again!
- Shock him again!

01:01.981 --> 01:05.293
- I'll do it my damn self!
- All right, all right, all right.

01:05.316 --> 01:06.862
- Let's go again.
- Hit him again!

01:06.886 --> 01:08.530
- Charging.
- (ELECTRICAL WHIRRING)

01:08.554 --> 01:09.931
- Come on, son.
- Clear.

01:09.955 --> 01:11.333
- Andre, please. - Hands off.
- Shocking.

01:11.357 --> 01:13.602
- Clear. - (ELECTRICAL THUMP)
- Oh, my God.

01:13.626 --> 01:16.560
(MONITOR CONTINUES FLATLINING)

01:18.330 --> 01:19.808
Come on, man.

01:19.832 --> 01:22.699
- Come on, son.
- Andre.

01:24.136 --> 01:26.048
(MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY)

01:26.072 --> 01:27.849
We have a rhythm and a pulse.

01:27.873 --> 01:30.619
(GASPS, CRYING)

01:30.643 --> 01:32.521
See, see, see.

01:32.545 --> 01:34.856
Don't you touch me!

01:34.880 --> 01:37.948
You tried to kill him!
You tried to kill my baby!

01:39.336 --> 01:44.876
