01:45.921 --> 01:48.905
What were you thinking? Hmm?

01:48.906 --> 01:50.751
You was just gonna
let Andre kill hisself?

01:50.775 --> 01:52.452
What, you wanted me
to let him die alone?

01:52.476 --> 01:54.688
Y'all need to just calm down, okay?

01:54.712 --> 01:55.923
No, he was suffering.

01:55.947 --> 01:58.058
Yeah, I couldn't even
talk his ass out of it.

01:58.082 --> 02:00.027
I would've talked him out of it.
You should've told me.

02:00.051 --> 02:01.762
He didn't want you to know!
He talked to me!

02:01.786 --> 02:04.531
- I'm his mother. -Hey, hey, hey.
Stop, stop, stop, hey. Hakeem.

02:04.555 --> 02:07.134
- Please come take your father.
- Yeah, take your father out of here.

02:07.158 --> 02:09.603
- I was trying to do the right thing.
- Come on, Dad.

02:09.627 --> 02:11.705
Yeah, you wouldn't know
the right thing if it was

02:11.729 --> 02:13.807
- staring you in the face, Lucious.
- Let's go.

02:13.831 --> 02:16.143
(SIGHS)

02:16.167 --> 02:17.411
(EXHALES)

02:17.435 --> 02:20.948
Andre must've been so scared.

02:20.972 --> 02:22.950
(BREATH SHUDDERING)

02:22.974 --> 02:27.788
I just, I just, I just see him
with all those pills, you know,

02:27.812 --> 02:30.223
and Lucious just standing there.

02:30.247 --> 02:31.925
CAROL: Sis, Lucious loves that boy.

02:31.949 --> 02:33.160
Real talk.

02:33.184 --> 02:34.761
In that moment, he was just a father

02:34.785 --> 02:36.229
trying to be there for his son.

02:36.253 --> 02:38.065
CANDACE AND COOKIE: Shut up, Carol.

02:38.089 --> 02:40.000
If Cookie hadn't come along
when she did, I hate to...

02:40.024 --> 02:42.436
- No, no, no, no, no.
- I...

02:42.460 --> 02:44.071
I don't want to think about that.

02:44.095 --> 02:46.740
(RINGTONE PLAYING)

02:46.764 --> 02:48.342
It's Jamal.

02:48.366 --> 02:50.944
Hey, baby. You on your way?

02:50.968 --> 02:52.145
What?

02:52.169 --> 02:54.648
Wait, what do you mean?

02:54.672 --> 02:57.084
Okay, boy, I'm calm. Just tell me.

02:57.108 --> 02:59.007
(QUIETLY): What now?

03:01.379 --> 03:05.092
Okay, I-I understand.
There's nothing you can do.

03:05.116 --> 03:08.762
Just stay safe, all right?
I got enough to think about.

03:08.786 --> 03:11.098
I love you. All right.

03:11.122 --> 03:12.466
Is he okay, sis?

03:12.490 --> 03:14.368
Yeah, he's fine. He's just...

03:14.392 --> 03:17.004
He's stuck at the Seychelles.
There's a storm.

03:17.028 --> 03:18.438
He can't get a flight out.

03:18.462 --> 03:21.108
(GROANS) So mad!

03:21.132 --> 03:24.811
- Can't even look at Lucious.
- I'd never look at him again.

03:24.835 --> 03:26.380
All right, Candace, that's not fair.

03:26.404 --> 03:27.881
Don't defend him.

03:27.905 --> 03:30.050
He wasn't even thinking about her.

03:30.074 --> 03:33.787
As usual, Lucious will
always be "Lucious."

03:33.811 --> 03:35.555
COOKIE: This time it's different.

03:35.579 --> 03:38.291
We're talking about my son's life.

03:38.315 --> 03:40.527
Sis, that's what you need to focus on.

03:40.551 --> 03:44.064
You know, Andre... he needs you
to be strong right now, sis.

03:44.088 --> 03:48.135
The doctors, they revived him,
but he still needs a new heart.

03:48.159 --> 03:50.392
He's in the fight of his life.

