Hi.

04:21.024 --> 04:22.335
(TERI SOBS SOFTLY)

04:22.359 --> 04:25.539
I wish you would've come to me.

04:25.563 --> 04:28.942
- Can't be angry, okay?
- I'm a nurse.

04:28.966 --> 04:30.911
Andre, I could've helped you
through this.

04:30.935 --> 04:32.279
Teri, I'm dying.

04:32.303 --> 04:34.848
I don't want to put you through that.

04:34.872 --> 04:38.907
I told you, this is not
the end of our story.

04:40.211 --> 04:42.945
It's just the beginning.

04:44.081 --> 04:46.114
My mom said you're pregnant.

04:48.619 --> 04:52.232
- We're having a baby?
- A son.

04:52.256 --> 04:54.234
- Boy?
- A boy.

04:54.258 --> 04:56.236
- (CHUCKLES)
- A son?

04:56.260 --> 04:58.972
WOMAN (OVER P.A.): Dr. White,
please call your office.

04:58.996 --> 05:01.208
Hey, how is he?

05:01.232 --> 05:03.376
He's awake.

05:03.400 --> 05:05.645
- That's a good sign.
- Man, shut up.

05:05.669 --> 05:09.082
Look, you stay with him.

05:09.106 --> 05:12.052
I'm gonna head back, and Giselle
and I are gonna figure out

05:12.076 --> 05:15.322
