cardiologist who could help.

05:35.766 --> 05:38.133
Cool. You should leave the card
with the nurse.

05:40.137 --> 05:42.682
I can call him right now
if you'd like.

05:42.706 --> 05:45.652
Your face is not the one
Moms want to see right now.

05:45.676 --> 05:48.977
You ain't family, so get out of here.

05:51.448 --> 05:54.650
Okay. Got it.

06:01.959 --> 06:04.804
I'm sorry. I-I didn't mean to intrude.

06:04.828 --> 06:07.340
No, no, Kingsley. I'm...

06:07.364 --> 06:09.865
- actually glad you came.
- (PATS CHAIR)

06:11.402 --> 06:13.380
Thanks for coming.

06:13.404 --> 06:16.316
Yeah.

06:16.340 --> 06:19.853
- I hear Andre's stable.
- Yeah, for now.

06:19.877 --> 06:22.122
Cookie won't let me
go anywhere near him.

06:22.146 --> 06:26.281
She just don't realize I would
give my heart for that boy.

06:32.389 --> 06:35.202
You know what?
You should get out of here.

06:35.226 --> 06:37.904
Clear your head. Give her some space.

06:37.928 --> 06:39.461
Come on.

06:41.432 --> 06:44.433
Yeah, that's a good idea.

06:46.203 --> 06:47.869
(SIGHS)

06:51.875 --> 06:54.710
