07:12.229 --> 07:15.100
Yeah, just... Tiana can open
and then throw it to Devon.

07:15.101 --> 07:16.712
Yeah, that works.

07:16.736 --> 07:20.850
Um, also, um, I know
we're in crisis right now,

07:20.851 --> 07:23.630
but I just want to be honest
with you about something.

07:23.654 --> 07:25.332
Go ahead.

07:25.356 --> 07:27.968
Okay, so, Def Jam offered me a job.

07:27.992 --> 07:31.071
- Ew.
- And, unless the Empire fans come back,

07:31.095 --> 07:32.872
I'm gonna be forced to take it.

07:32.896 --> 07:36.617
And walk away from all this
Black Girl Magic? (SCOFFS)

07:36.641 --> 07:38.712
Okay, but is this Black Girl
Magic gonna pay my rent?

07:38.736 --> 07:39.913
'Cause it's not.

07:39.937 --> 07:42.640
Look, the test of whether
the fans come back

07:42.641 --> 07:44.819
is based on the relaunch
of Empire XStream

07:44.843 --> 07:46.821
after our final concert, right?

07:46.845 --> 07:49.691
Yes, but that's if
the apology tour actually works.

07:49.715 --> 07:52.427
Of course the fans will be
willing to subscribe again.

07:52.451 --> 07:54.362
So all we have to do is come up
with the right incentives.

07:54.386 --> 07:56.519
There ain't gonna be
no incentives that...

07:58.490 --> 08:00.301
Think.

08:00.325 --> 08:01.803
Huh.

08:01.827 --> 08:05.173
How about we release a compilation

08:05.197 --> 08:07.442
of the live Trust Tour performances?

08:07.466 --> 08:10.712
Making it exclusive to XStream
with videos from the tour

08:10.736 --> 08:13.514
and exclusive backstage footage

08:13.538 --> 08:15.183
and the promise of more every month.

08:15.207 --> 08:18.219
Exactly, because if they love
the Trust Tour so much,

08:18.243 --> 08:19.620
they're gonna want
to reminisce about it,

08:19.644 --> 08:20.855
and that they would be...

08:20.879 --> 08:22.290
BOTH: ...willing to pay for!

08:22.314 --> 08:23.725
Bitch, we got this.

08:23.749 --> 08:26.561
- We're so smart. We're geniuses.
- (CLICKS TONGUE)

08:26.585 --> 08:28.418
Well, mostly me.

08:32.190 --> 08:34.224
You mad at me, too?

08:36.027 --> 08:39.307
Lord knows I want to be so bad,

08:39.331 --> 08:43.099
but I am too happy that you're alive.

08:44.402 --> 08:47.682
So you were really
trying to say goodbye to me

08:47.706 --> 08:49.739
at the roller skating rink, Andre?

08:52.043 --> 08:54.655
I wish you would've told me
what was going on.

08:54.679 --> 08:56.090
Would you have agreed to help me?

08:56.114 --> 08:58.259
Help you kill yours...

08:58.283 --> 09:00.495
Hell no, boy.

09:00.519 --> 09:02.563
Look, Andre, if you can't
fight for yourself,

09:02.587 --> 09:04.232
then I will fight for you.

09:04.256 --> 09:06.667
I don't know what the hell
Lucious was thinking.

09:06.691 --> 09:08.102
Don't blame him, Ma.

09:08.126 --> 09:11.539
He was only doing what I asked,
and that comes from love, too.

09:11.563 --> 09:13.374
It does.

09:13.398 --> 09:16.511
- We can't beat this, Ma.
- Mm-mm.

09:16.535 --> 09:19.747
I don't want to hear that, okay?

09:19.771 --> 09:22.583
Miracles happen every day, baby.
You got to have hope.

09:22.607 --> 09:23.951
Miracles don't happen for me, Ma.

09:23.975 --> 09:26.687
Andre, you are not going to die.

09:26.711 --> 09:28.289
- (SNAPS FINGERS)
- Okay?

09:28.313 --> 09:30.424
Mm-mm.

09:30.448 --> 09:32.248
Not on my watch.

09:33.251 --> 09:35.652
Not on my watch.

09:38.423 --> 09:40.456
(HORNS HONKING,
SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE)

09:43.161 --> 09:44.605
