09:44.629 --> 09:46.140
- What up, baby?
- Hey.

09:46.164 --> 09:47.575
Mr. Lucious, how you doing today?

09:47.599 --> 09:50.244
- Hey, you got any of my stuff in here?
- I got all this.

09:50.268 --> 09:52.246
Check it out.

09:52.270 --> 09:55.249
- (LAUGHS)
- Wow.

09:55.273 --> 10:00.254
Something about the vinyl
I can't just pass up.

10:00.278 --> 10:01.455
Oh, yeah?

10:01.479 --> 10:03.758
Yeah, when that needle hits the...

10:03.782 --> 10:06.394
